Source: pg-stat-ch
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), cmake, g++, ninja-build, libssl-dev, pkg-config, protobuf-compiler, protobuf-compiler-grpc, libprotobuf-dev, libgrpc++-dev, libabsl-dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/ClickHouse/pg_stat_ch

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-stat-ch
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-stat-ch
Depends: postgresql-PGVERSION, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Query telemetry exporter to ClickHouse for PostgreSQL
  pg_stat_ch captures detailed per-query execution telemetry from PostgreSQL
  and exports it to ClickHouse in real time.
  This recipe builds the extension from source for PostgreSQL 16 through 18.
